data.description: MOVE IN BEFORE CHRISTMAS…AND BE HOME FOR THE HOLIDAYS!!  ***Seller offering a one point buydown or VA assumable loan*** Please inquire for more details. Welcome to a rare find in the heart of the Cheverly community—a meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bath Spanish Mission style home. The main floor of this home boasts an open-concept design, creating a spacious and welcoming atmosphere filled with natural light. Recent window installations throughout the main floor illuminate the interior, creating a warm and inviting environment. You'll also discover a wood-burning fireplace complemented by stunning wood floors. The kitchen is a true highlight, featuring beautiful countertops and modern appliances.  Venture to the basement, where you'll find a guest room or 4th bedroom and a full bathroom. The basement also offers ample space for entertaining friends and family.   A new heating and air conditioning system was installed just weeks ago, ensuring your year-round comfort.  Outside, you'll be pleasantly surprised by the screened-in-back deck and the comfortable backyard, a rarity in this area. Additionally, the property features a driveway and garage, providing convenient and secure parking—a true luxury in the Cheverly neighborhood.  For those with a daily commute, you'll appreciate the easy access to major routes such as 202, 295, Rt 50, and Cheverly Metro. This central location makes getting to Joint Base Andrews, The Pentagon, Washington Navy Yard, and Fort George G Mead a breeze.  In your free time, you'll have a wealth of options. The Cheverly Swim & Racquet Club, Cheverly Metro, and the Farmers Market are just a stone's throw away. Access to downtown DC, Capitol Hill, Hyattsville Art District, UMD, and an array of shopping options, including Dakota Crossing (Lowes, Costco, Starbucks), Woodmore Town Center (Wegmans and more), and Landover Road (Aldi, Walgreens), is incredibly convenient.  Cheverly is a community with a vibrant social scene. There's a group, club, or organization to suit every interest. Don't miss the annual Cheverly Day festivities. Lastly, for peace of mind when you're away, the Cheverly Police Department offers a home check service to ensure your property and belongings are safe and sound. Learn more about Cheverly at cheverly-md.gov  Don't let this exceptional opportunity slip away. Schedule a viewing today and experience the unique charm and convenience this property has to offer.
